Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll resume. Can you all hear me? We'll resume and I'm going to sign books and as I sign books
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,people will ask questions and I'll answer them, not as complexly as we did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We just calibrated the level of aesthetics because in a way aesthetics are part of the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,partial answer to some of the questions. Aesthetics becomes a prominent part of the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,human psyche around calibrated level 360. Just beyond Chinese fortune cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.59,0:01:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aesthetics. So you know many could give many answers to the questions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but one of the appreciations of life is the awareness of beauty and the part that it plays
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in your decision making and your values of life. You know we saw a dog during the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,lunch break, stunningly beautiful, this black stunning dog. Not only its lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but its stunning beauty you know and so you begin to appreciate the beauty of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you blindfold somebody and take their blindfold off I can tell you the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,level of where I am by looking about two feet around me because when you're in certain dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,parts of the world they all look the same. There's litter, there's trash, there's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,graffiti, there's a complete lack of appreciation for beauty and when you see the emergence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of respect for beauty then salvation is not far. So in answer to a question that came
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,up this morning, what can we do for the children individually and collectively? I think teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.06,0:02:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,them the appreciation of aesthetics. If I look back at my own childhood what the visual
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,do I value most? Well, Midwest lifestyle of the 30s, etc., had a certain profound inner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,value of itself. But the things that accrued to that was an intense appreciation for beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of its forms. So the fortunate part of my own lifetime was my parents were musical,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,my father was a musician. We were all very sensitive to aesthetics and traditional religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,To be in a great cathedral, there I am a boy soprano singing Pontus Angelicus with a full
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,orchestra in a full cathedral, with the stained glass windows and a full choir and a full
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,audience hanging on every obbligato-soprano note. It was ethereal. It was like unreal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and it imprinted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It imprints beauty. So one of the expressions of divinity is aesthetics and beauty. And
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the answer to the gentleman's question, what can we do for the children that are under
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,such assault by that which is non-integrative in our society, is to expose them to real
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,beauty and aesthetics. The appreciation for opera. As a boy, I listened on Saturday afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Milton Krauss from the Metropolitan Opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, I knew all about the Nibelungen Ring and the Wagner and the Bizet, all those
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,things just as a boy, as a boy. So if I had to do it over again, I would express as much
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,energy as I can in directing the children in aesthetics. Ballet dancing, there's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,more exquisite than seeing a pas de deux from a great ballet, you know. And we have tickets
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,for it this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The only time I rode to Phoenix to see La Boheme, you know, in the spring, or a great
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,ballet, the Sadler-Wells Ballet. So in a small town, in Wisconsin, which I'm sure from the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,viewpoint of LA or New York is the sticks, we never missed a thing, you see, because
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,we didn't take it for granted. So when the Sadler-Wells Ballet came through or when,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, Paderewski came through or Gala Kirche or somebody great came through, we
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,went.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So the answer then I wanted to give was aesthetics would be the counterbalance to ugliness. So
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the dominion of ugliness is negated by the inner appreciation of beauty, because once
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you have an inner appreciation of beauty, ugliness stands forth as ugliness. And it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,may be stylish, it may be hip, it may be cool, but the fact that it's ugly is quite obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Teaching our children aesthetics and communicating…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,…and communicating our appreciation and love and value of aesthetics, I think is probably
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the best counter for us, a counterbalance we can give to ugliness and the danger of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,ugliness to the psyche of the children. I know you didn't ask me, but I know you'd
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's proceed, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:06:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can say, you know, my obligation to you is to be that which I am to the greatest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,extent as I can be to a greater extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to you, to be radically all that I can be, and thus serve you is my joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would like to thank you personally, and this is a token of my appreciation of all the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,good things you've done for me this year and for everyone else. This is the latest Robert Gass CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the music we listen to, Kyrie and Alleluia. Yes, he's wonderful. This is his
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,latest and greatest, and I'd like to offer it to you as a Christmas offering. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. Yes. First, thank you very much again. I have not been very comfortable with
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibration or the kinesiological process. I was hoping that you might do two calibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:07:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,for me if you'd have a problem. No. You'd have a problem. All right. There's a spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,teacher in India by the name of Gurinder Singh, and I'm curious where he
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates. I'm curious where he calibrates. I'm curious where he calibrates. I'm curious where
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,his teachings calibrate at. I can't really do that right now. You know, we prepared quite a huge
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,volume about it. To answer these things correctly, they have to be contextualized in a certain way
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so as to avoid judgmentalism. See? Otherwise, you think 440 is better than 420. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily so, because the task of 440 is different than the task of 220.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not better than. Each level of consciousness addresses its own level.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a person at 420 can be an excellent teacher at 420, and somebody at 480 can be a very bad teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see, the excellence is on its own level. So, I can say, well, Einstein only reached 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:08:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, 499, the Einstein level that he reached, you know, has changed the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it isn't just a calibrated level of consciousness, but the whole contextualization of it and the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,timing of it. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess what my intent is, it's not so much to place a judgment on where he is as much as a protection
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm not with the charlatan one way or the other. And, I mean, I don't feel that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, more my curiosity is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's been 20 years, and I haven't, you know, there's four requirements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth one being initiation, which he gives you a mantra.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've danced around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not made that plunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you in a different way later and not in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See, what you really want to know is the appropriateness of where you're at is really the question you're asking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, by that you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the reason you're asking me the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the appropriateness of where you're at and the step you want to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not asking me about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a different question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll answer you afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, is a certain move appropriate for where you're at at a given time is really the question you're asking, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with him, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because at the wrong time, Jesus is the wrong person to worship, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you'd be seeing him in a way that would not be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you can send these books.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I just really enjoy being in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I feel that my mind is quiet when I'm close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I give you a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, he's got a lot of muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out when you scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's a mesomorph.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I once had a buddy, and he'd had a couple of beers, and he dropped in to visit me, and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,he gave me a big hug and broke three of them on one side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't tell him, because I knew it would hurt his feelings, and he'd feel guilty about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just kept it to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I tell him, go, crump, crump, crump.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a tough winter, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To celebrate, I went country riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to a lot of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to a lot of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to a lot of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to a lot of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to Western dancing, and I turned this girl who's called a dip, I think, to go underneath
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She ducked under her arm, or she missed, and her head hit me, my ribs on the other side,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and broke them on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:11:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was busted rib winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,First three on one side, then three on the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I went to see an orthopedist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, what is this with the busted ribs all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, you need more calcium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've been taking calcium ever since, and I haven't broken a rib since.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm careful who I hug, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening when you have a spontaneous movement out of form, and then you get pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Years go by, maybe it happens, I guess, two, three times versus working at this and getting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because that's the way it usually comes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like feelings, like you'll suddenly out of nowhere have a presence of light within
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself, and it illuminates all things, and you're beyond all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stunning, and it's very distinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the next day, it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, well, where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the great night of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, where hast thou gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What have I done wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How come thou hast deserted me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Christian saints, you know, the bridegroom, what have you left me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the wings of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And they soar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And what you see is your own destiny ahead, that's your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just go back to doing what you're doing and working your spiritual program to the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,best of your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it becomes more and more predominant, but it may come very intensely and leave a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,number of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it first came on to me at age three, then it came on again at age 12 in the snowbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it came recurrently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:13:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And it would leave for five or six years, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I learned, do not pine for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do whatever you're doing with the same devotion and stop looking for dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say, oh, Lord, let me surrender my appetite for that delicious dessert and serve you during
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the ordinary meal of everyday life, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in that state, you can't function anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're useless as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You sit there smiling sweetly at everybody, embracing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray for peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So it could be that you've got something else of equal importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only to tell you that, yes, you are on the pathway, and it gives you like a preliminary
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,assurance of the reality of that level of reality, that even if you experience it for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.17,0:13:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds, you now know it, and it leaves an imprint in your consciousness that will never
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, it leaves a vibrational frequency in your aura, and it doesn't ever forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Never forgets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never be satisfied with anything less.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you elaborate on the psychic attacks that you endured and how you endured them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychic attacks were something I didn't believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded very New Age-y and yah, yah, yah, baloney stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was only when they became...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only when they became severe, then I used the diagnostic consciousness techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to discern what it is, and also through prayer, how to undo it, what the error is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond a certain level, consciousness is like you're not allowed to hang on to an error.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like your commitment has already demanded that you let go of that error.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of that error.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of that error.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I found that anguishing, it didn't happen up to a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain level was exquisite bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was miraculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was love and exquisite beauty and oneness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then beyond that, I forget what started the movement beyond that, but then started
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the feeling of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like that which you have become is viewed as competitively dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,dangerous for the dominion over mankind. When you start unveiling the lies and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you start taking the sheep's clothing off the wolf, you start to get bitten. And
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was distressed by it. I found how to transcend it to find out what
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,chakra in which archetype was out about what. And through prayer and forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and asking God to see it differently, then I would feel that pain leave me. But
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it was like your whole body was on fire with a sub-lethal level of electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it wasn't enough to kill you. They slowly fried you. So we were in Korea
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,when Susan found the answer. She pulled out. I said, God, what is this? What is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,this? What is this? And she reached in the drawer, pulled out the equivalent of the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Christian Bible, a book of verses, and she ripped it out of the drawer. And Jesus
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddhist Bible, and she opened the page, and it says, the Buddha said that he, on his way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to enlightenment, he was wracked with pain and attacked by the demons, and attacked by
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the demons and wracked with pain, like his bones were broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly, I felt better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, that's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what is going, or what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now, instead of feeling bad about it, you say, well, you've chosen this, and now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, the human nervous system isn't made for that kind of consciousness level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The human nervous system is comfortable up to about 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond that, it's not, the human nervous system is not made to handle those frequencies and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,those high energies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the nervous system, in this case, the nervous system had to actually become
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,heavier by accretion of proteins and various other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The nervous system literally had to adapt to the taxation of that energy frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finished doing that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:17:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finished doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finished doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finished doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, putting 220 volts through 110 wiring system, I guess, is the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, it's adapted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It has now adapted to that requirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's first of God, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But hearing that from the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, sharing our spiritual experience with each other, see how meaningful it is to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For all of us to hear of others' experiences, you know, we all benefit to know that that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,advanced glimpse of what's coming up spiritually in the future for you can come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When it happens to you and it goes, you say, well, I've heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're getting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes and then it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And not to feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to feel bad about it, that you've done something wrong, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to hear of it, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the minute she read from the book, I felt instantly better, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's not something commonly spoken of in our society, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a psychiatrist 50 years and I never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I read all the great intellects of all time and I never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, hear an obscure Bible in a drawer in a hotel in South Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There was the answer, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you say, dear God, you know, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,God leads your wife to open the drawer and she pulls it out and she says, here's what
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the Buddha said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That was very nice of the Buddha to leave the message for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And what it has to do with, I guess, is when you spoke about, or when you speak about enforcing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or enforced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were talking about sobriety earlier, enforced sobriety.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, enforced, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you, are you, is that, are you speaking the same way as when you speak of force?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, karmic, you know, what's traditionally called good karma, only comes about as a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,result of your own personal choice, not because you're coerced to some move by somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, in the beginning, you could be coerced by somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And later, of volition, by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That happens to people in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're put in prison, and there they go through a transformation of consciousness, and some
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,reach almost sainthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was out of the choice of free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, it wasn't their free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as some people who get sent to 12-step groups, say, A, by the judge, and they've
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,got to have other people sign that they attended.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the beginning, it may be with resentment, and then much to their own surprise, suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,they become an enthusiast.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're a genuine member.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But of their own free choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So that ties in with discipline?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I like how.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really what I'm wondering about, is that I have a belief that not eating meat
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is probably better than eating meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know this because I'm not a vegetarian, but from a perspective, I can see that as
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I tend to think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That that is a process that comes, and that the desire for and the tolerance of meat falls
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,away, versus a choice just to become a vegetarian out of a discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:22:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So at various times, depending on where you are and your level of understanding, it means
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,different things, and therefore your behavior would mean different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At one point, it would be adherence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a Buddhist, strict Buddhist, you know, I kept the butterfly net.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I would sit behind the grapes in my office, and between patients, I would take the butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.05,0:22:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,net and catch the flies and put them out the window, because I didn't want to swat one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.91,0:22:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In those days, I believed in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Death was a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought, if I'm killing the fly, I'm killing life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you think that you can kill life, then you shouldn't be killing life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you realize that life cannot be killed, to the fly, it doesn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.57,0:22:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So it all depends on how you're seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, see, each level...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're expressing the reality of where you were at spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,See, while you think of this, you should be doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.48,0:22:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,While you're doing this, you should be doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.11,0:22:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:23:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess I still have input from different levels at the same, maybe not the exact same
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,moment, but from moment, or a relatively short moment to moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.68,0:23:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's not a linear process.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a non-linear process.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And so one day, you see this scintillation more than this scintillation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I was sitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sitting at dinner, and they say, what do you want, steak or fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I always order fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, I looked at my meat, and I said, I am meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.52,0:23:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have steak, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing the cow a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't eat steak, there's going to be no cows out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Millions of cattle will not have a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.72,0:23:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So it all depends on how you contextualize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I completely understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can serve life by eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:24:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as I said before, the Rig Veda says that each level of life is sacrificial to that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,above it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you reward the animal by allowing, by when you eat the animal, you're allowing it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.03,0:24:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to evolve to a higher level of consciousness by uniting with you and your blessedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.55,0:24:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And in so doing, you bless the animal, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.01,0:24:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it depends on how you wish you envision it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.94,0:24:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give you half a dozen of the ways, but that's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.98,0:24:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.03,0:24:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I'm wondering now, then, because I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.98,0:24:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.77,0:24:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.61,0:24:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I do understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.00,0:24:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.64,0:24:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to walk away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.27,0:24:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.68,0:24:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the should.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.74,0:24:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a should that's coming out of ego or judgment or something that I'm still working
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.94,0:24:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.14,0:24:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The should that eating meat is not a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.42,0:24:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.57,0:24:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't eat it while it's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.05,0:24:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a good thing, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.77,0:24:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.55,0:24:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.51,0:24:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.42,0:25:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of the things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.81,0:25:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Money, sex, eating meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.29,0:25:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the big ones that hit all spiritual students.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.50,0:25:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Money, sex, work, eating meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.88,0:25:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the traditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.50,0:25:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.00,0:25:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.66,0:25:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question on the chart that you put up earlier, and this probably comes straight
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.05,0:25:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,from my mammalian ego, but could you account for the difference in calibration between
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.48,0:25:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.48,0:25:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chimpanzees as a species, which you say calibrated around 400 and...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.24,0:25:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say it's a species they calibrated 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.00,0:25:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.93,0:25:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I said cocoa reached 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.97,0:25:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Cocoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.11,0:25:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Cocoa is a gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.83,0:25:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take dairy cattle then.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.51,0:25:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.14,0:25:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.74,0:25:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dairy cattle, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.38,0:25:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that about...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.16,0:25:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In the 200s.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.61,0:25:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,250 or so, if I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.48,0:25:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.01,0:25:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.75,0:25:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Herbivores.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.18,0:25:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And mankind as a species calibrates now at 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.44,0:26:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.00,0:26:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fox News instead of ABC, that's my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.26,0:26:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.17,0:26:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the problem is that you're trying to understand many things with the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.44,0:26:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect is not the right tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.79,0:26:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Observation and intuition would be a better way, because then the significance of it dawns
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.14,0:26:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,on you as you're driving along, not even thinking about it, you suddenly see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.59,0:26:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect is not the right tool to understand many things about consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.33,0:26:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.50,0:26:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.82,0:26:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.23,0:26:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.25,0:26:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.26,0:26:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.28,0:26:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.34,0:26:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.39,0:26:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.41,0:26:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.43,0:26:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.47,0:26:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.49,0:26:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.50,0:26:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.54,0:26:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.56,0:26:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.78,0:26:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.82,0:26:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.84,0:26:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.91,0:26:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.13,0:26:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.21,0:26:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.76,0:26:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.86,0:26:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.23,0:26:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.58,0:26:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.78,0:26:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.91,0:26:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.10,0:26:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.13,0:26:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.21,0:26:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.30,0:26:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.39,0:26:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.47,0:26:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.56,0:26:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.60,0:26:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.80,0:26:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.82,0:26:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.71,0:26:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.08,0:26:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that's what the...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.65,0:27:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that isn't what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.47,0:27:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.58,0:27:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I said the Rig Vida states, Krishna states, that each level sacrifices itself to the evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.73,0:27:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of life by serving the next level.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.58,0:27:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that's what the Rig Vida says.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.40,0:27:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So do these levels...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.42,0:27:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I said the Rig Vida says.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.25,0:27:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, the Rig Veda said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.57,0:27:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think these levels correspond to the calibrated levels of consciousness or of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.50,0:27:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.32,0:27:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the levels referred to in the Rig Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.63,0:27:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,correspond to the calibrated levels of the species that you had on the chart earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.15,0:27:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I would imagine, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.15,0:27:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,God created the animals and he created the humans and he created the fishes and the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.55,0:27:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to my original question about humanity calibrating at 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.85,0:27:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.33,0:28:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And a dairy cow calibrating at 245, which is the lower level.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.55,0:28:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, some humanity calibrates lower than cattle?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.07,0:28:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, of course they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.90,0:28:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.05,0:28:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been in a Nazi torture camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.79,0:28:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.77,0:28:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you won't have any question about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.59,0:28:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole civilizations calibrate at 60 and 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.82,0:28:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize there's whole civilizations where you would be executed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.98,0:28:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even having challenged me with a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.35,0:28:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.72,0:28:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're a brave man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.22,0:28:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.19,0:28:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's been brave.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.96,0:29:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have the potentiality of reaching a level in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.27,0:29:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.96,0:29:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The content of your question is not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.68,0:29:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is using the wrong tool to address it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.16,0:29:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that these things are going to fall within explicable logic or reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.53,0:29:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.79,0:29:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They just are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.79,0:29:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They are what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.90,0:29:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The inference of it only sort of dawns on you, but it does it in a sort of a non-logical way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.76,0:29:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that a donkey calibrates higher than a lot of people on the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.13,0:29:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in the planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.97,0:29:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.47,0:29:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A donkey's harmless, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.63,0:29:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safer with a donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.02,0:29:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safer with Coco, the gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.00,0:29:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take you to neighborhoods in New York City that are far less safe than being in a cage with Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.22,0:29:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's the only gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.77,0:29:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog I met at lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.09,0:29:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.90,0:29:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Loving, friendly, trusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.90,0:30:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.74,0:30:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.77,0:30:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.71,0:30:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.21,0:30:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.59,0:30:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.00,0:30:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's a pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.90,0:30:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes up in public and gives you a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.51,0:30:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, who...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.40,0:30:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good friend, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.11,0:30:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody can come up and just be friendly and I'll get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.11,0:30:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.61,0:30:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy going.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.31,0:30:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy going.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.83,0:30:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy going.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.68,0:30:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy going.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.18,0:30:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.69,0:30:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.58,0:30:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trained to rely on the intellect to solve our problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.65,0:30:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's hard to get that the intellect will only take you so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.59,0:31:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Many years ago, first reading about Buddhism and Zen and all, in the great dismay, I discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.68,0:31:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that trying harder won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.98,0:31:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Studying harder, reading more books and trying harder wasn't the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.96,0:31:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember the feeling of defeat because the intellect is what I spent all these years
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.72,0:31:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,perfecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.96,0:31:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I'm told
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.67,0:31:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,they won't do me any good
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.69,0:31:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a follow up question
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.43,0:31:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to the free will question
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.32,0:31:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.32,0:31:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,explained that all things happen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.34,0:31:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,spontaneously according
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.17,0:31:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to its karmic propensity
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.84,0:31:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so do we choose at the level
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.49,0:31:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,of form that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.45,0:31:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you can pick up that pen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.13,0:31:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it a more abstract level
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.10,0:31:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that you choose truth or illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.47,0:31:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,not in the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.26,0:31:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,physical world
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.21,0:31:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,for potentiality become actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.38,0:31:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.03,0:31:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in a generic way it depends on
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.23,0:31:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,intention
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.95,0:32:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in a generic way
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.24,0:32:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in the ultimate generic
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.94,0:32:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,way it's
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.99,0:32:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the expression of
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.71,0:32:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of divinity itself
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.63,0:32:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of divinity is such
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.97,0:32:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that anything you put in
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.14,0:32:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,its field
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.79,0:32:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,its potentiality now is
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.77,0:32:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,realizable
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.51,0:32:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,as an actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.61,0:32:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,just like magnetism
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.59,0:32:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,on an iron filing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.51,0:32:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not personal
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.00,0:32:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but the quality of the field
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.82,0:32:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is for that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.67,0:32:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,which has potential
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.23,0:32:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to mature
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.02,0:32:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to mature
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.86,0:32:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so is it my free will
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.20,0:32:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to walk up here
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.64,0:32:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,or was my free will
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.38,0:32:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,at a different level
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.46,0:32:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,did this just arise spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.50,0:32:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that you're here means that that was
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.29,0:32:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a potentiality that was realized
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.25,0:32:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,before you were here and that's why you're here now
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.38,0:32:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not possible as an actuality
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.72,0:32:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but only your intention made it happen
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.22,0:32:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so my choice is my intention as well
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.16,0:32:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,right
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.68,0:32:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's all intention
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.31,0:33:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it's intention not the action
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.33,0:33:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the action is just
