Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.96,0:55:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Power corrupts absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.96,0:55:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why even somebody like Mohammed, see, once he gets a certain amount of power, unless
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.13,0:55:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you're trained how to handle that power, it takes you over.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.78,0:55:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes you over.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.78,0:55:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes you over.
