Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.73,1:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.73,1:05:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.36,1:05:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can still walk, we'll close up just at 4 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.26,1:05:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we will sign the remaining books.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.11,1:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.40,1:05:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Maui, and when we spin with the whales and the dolphins,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.03,1:05:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,we feel the way we feel when we chance and when you speak,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.13,1:05:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't understand it, but thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.53,1:05:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.88,1:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No question it means you've heard me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.25,1:05:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.94,1:05:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard me, there's no question it's love.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.30,1:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.59,1:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.86,1:07:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so, then love for our fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.84,1:07:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be out of here at the requested time of 4 o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.13,1:07:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,just as we started at the requested time of 9 o'clock,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.76,1:07:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,out of love for our fellow humans,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.11,1:07:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that we respect their time,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.25,1:07:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the personages of their time,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.90,1:07:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.65,1:07:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that love takes many expressions.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.94,1:07:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only cleaning up the trash on the street,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.78,1:07:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but being on time because everybody makes an effort to be here,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.09,1:07:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore our obligation out of love
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.61,1:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is to respect that effort on your part.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.76,1:07:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see how the mutual recognition
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.92,1:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,springs forth of its own nature, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.00,1:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, I'm very blessed to have been here with you this year,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.94,1:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in this place.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.88,1:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank the Radisson.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.05,1:07:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been very gracious to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.11,1:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They provided a very beautiful venue,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.76,1:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,wonderful lunches, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.05,1:07:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And plenty of parking space.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.26,1:08:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They were thankful for them for providing for us
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.15,1:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,such a wondrous place,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.86,1:08:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and this wonderful holiday decorations,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.03,1:08:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,nameless holiday decorations.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.42,1:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank you all for being with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.01,1:08:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who wish,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.19,1:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess have already gotten the brochure
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.93,1:08:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of the next year's lectures.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.06,1:08:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing them in Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.43,1:08:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing them every two months.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.14,1:08:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason we only do them every two months
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.07,1:08:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of monthly is because we do a lot of traveling now.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.89,1:08:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, at least once or twice a month,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.50,1:08:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,we travel someplace in the country
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.02,1:08:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and address pretty sizable audiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.51,1:08:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, that is a privilege as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.55,1:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we spend a lot of time on the road now,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.21,1:08:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore, we cut down to every two months.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.72,1:08:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the old home group, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.06,1:08:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.18,1:08:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Like your home boy scout troop, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.10,1:08:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own grade school class.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.14,1:09:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we have a certain feeling of family about each other already,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.30,1:09:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, certain family, feeling of family.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.02,1:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure comically, you know, if we saw the sweep of it all,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.14,1:09:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we sweep in and out as a family.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.53,1:09:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have done so many times, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.65,1:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.18,1:09:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you for being here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.39,1:09:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you for all your love.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.18,1:09:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm very grateful for it now and forever. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.10,1:09:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're wonderful audiences.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.35,1:09:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you help?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.55,1:09:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be the state of joy, because we're here basically.
